| 3 | No rate limiting | A04: Insecure Design | 🔴 High | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| 4 | No authentication on `/users` | A01: Broken Access Control | 🔴 High | Add auth middleware |
| 5 | PII in API response | A02: Sensitive Data Exposure | 🟠 Medium | Minimize returned fields |
| 6 | No explicit CORS policy | A05: Misconfiguration | 🟠 Medium | Add `cors` with allowlist |
| 7 | No error handling | A05: Misconfiguration | 🟠 Medium | Add error middleware |
| 8 | Hardcoded configuration | A05: Misconfiguration | 🟠 Medium | Use `dotenv` |
| 9 | No request logging | A09: Logging Failures | 🟡 Low | Add `morgan`/`pino` |
| 10 | Server fingerprinting | A05: Misconfiguration | 🟡 Low | Disable `x-powered-by` |

