| A02 – Cryptographic Failures | 🟠 | PII (emails) served over potentially unencrypted channel |
| A03 – Injection | 🟡 | No input parsing yet, but no validation framework in place |
| A04 – Insecure Design | 🟠 | No security middleware, no defense-in-depth |
| A05 – Security Misconfiguration | 🔴 | No helmet, no CORS, `x-powered-by` exposed |
| A06 – Vulnerable Components | ⚪ | No `package.json` found — cannot audit dependencies |
